{
  "_comment": "Holehe-Stil E-Mail-Account-Existenz-Checks + Such-/Dork-Links. account_sites: keyfreie Quellen mit KLAREM Signal (Einzelrequest). Pro Site: exists/notexists = Liste von Regeln (ANY trifft). Regeltypen: {status:[..]}, {body_equals:'..'}, {body_contains:'..'}, {json:'a.b', in:[..]}, {json:'a.b', eq:X}, {json_nonempty:'a.b'}, {all:[regel,..]} (alle muessen passen). Trifft weder exists noch notexists => INCONCLUSIVE (kein Treffer, kein sauberer Miss). Token-/CSRF-basierte Quellen (Strava/eBay/Amazon/Tumblr) sind als dedizierte zweistufige Handler im Modul email_osint.py implementiert (erst Seite holen + Token scrapen, dann pruefen) und werten ebenfalls nur das eindeutige Exists-Signal.",
  "account_sites": [
    {
      "name": "Microsoft / Office 365",
      "category": "Microsoft",
      "method": "POST",
      "url": "https://login.microsoftonline.com/common/GetCredentialType?mkt=en-US",
      "content_type": "json",
      "headers": {
        "Content-Type": "application/json; charset=utf-8",
        "Accept": "application/json",
        "Origin": "https://login.microsoftonline.com",
        "Referer": "https://login.microsoftonline.com/"
      },
      "body": {
        "username": "{email}",
        "isOtherIdpSupported": true,
        "checkPhones": false,
        "isRemoteNGCSupported": true,
        "isCookieBannerShown": false,
        "isFidoSupported": true,
        "originalRequest": "",
        "country": "US",
        "forceotclogin": false,
        "isExternalFederationDisallowed": false,
        "isRemoteConnectSupported": false,
        "federationFlags": 0,
        "isSignup": false,
        "flowToken": "",
        "isAccessPassSupported": true
      },
      "exists": [{"json": "IfExistsResult", "in": [0, 5, 6]}],
      "notexists": [{"json": "IfExistsResult", "in": [1]}],
      "extract": ["IfExistsResult", "ThrottleStatus", "IsUnmanaged"],
      "reliability": "high",
      "notes": "Microsoft Credential-Type-Enumeration. IfExistsResult 0/5/6 = Konto existiert (5/6 = foederiert), 1 = existiert nicht, 2 = throttled (unklar). Funktioniert fuer Consumer- und Azure-AD/M365-Konten."
    },
    {
      "name": "Spotify",
      "category": "Music",
      "method": "GET",
      "url": "https://spclient.wg.spotify.com/signup/public/v1/account?validate=1&email={emaillower}&country=US",
      "content_type": "none",
      "headers": {"Accept": "application/json"},
      "exists": [{"json": "status", "in": [20]}],
      "notexists": [{"json": "status", "in": [1]}],
      "reliability": "medium",
      "notes": "Signup-Validate-Endpoint: status 20 = E-Mail bereits registriert, 1 = verfuegbar."
    },
    {
      "name": "Any.do",
      "category": "Productivity",
      "method": "POST",
      "url": "https://sm-prod2.any.do/check_email",
      "content_type": "json",
      "headers": {
        "Accept": "*/*",
        "Content-Type": "application/json; charset=UTF-8",
        "X-Platform": "3",
        "Origin": "https://desktop.any.do",
        "Referer": "https://desktop.any.do/"
      },
      "body": {"email": "{email}"},
      "exists": [{"all": [{"status": [200]}, {"json": "user_exists", "eq": true}]}],
      "notexists": [{"all": [{"status": [200]}, {"json": "user_exists", "eq": false}]}],
      "reliability": "high"
    },
    {
      "name": "Plurk",
      "category": "Social Media",
      "method": "POST",
      "url": "https://www.plurk.com/Users/isEmailFound",
      "content_type": "form",
      "headers": {
        "Accept": "*/*",
        "Content-Type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
        "X-Requested-With": "XMLHttpRequest",
        "Origin": "https://www.plurk.com"
      },
      "body": "email={email}",
      "exists": [{"body_equals": "true"}],
      "notexists": [{"body_equals": "false"}],
      "reliability": "high"
    },
    {
      "name": "Twitter / X",
      "category": "Social Media",
      "method": "GET",
      "url": "https://api.twitter.com/i/users/email_available.json?email={email}",
      "content_type": "none",
      "headers": {"Accept": "application/json"},
      "exists": [{"json": "taken", "eq": true}],
      "notexists": [{"json": "taken", "eq": false}],
      "reliability": "low",
      "notes": "Legacy-Endpoint, von X oft geblockt (403) -> dann INCONCLUSIVE."
    },
    {
      "name": "mail.ru",
      "category": "Email Provider",
      "method": "POST",
      "url": "https://account.mail.ru/api/v1/user/password/restore",
      "content_type": "form",
      "headers": {
        "Accept": "application/json, text/javascript, */*; q=0.01",
